But it&#39;s difficult to compare reading speed and comprehension between
a script that&#39;s familiar from decades of daily use and one that has
only recently been learned. We&#39;d have to do experimental trials with
first-graders (or even younger) to find out, and even then QS is at a
disadvantage.

Ted


